1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 11=

11
00:01:00,159 --> 00:01:01,159
Su Wubing.

12
00:01:03,719 --> 00:01:04,680
You guys...

13
00:01:06,959 --> 00:01:07,760
Ningxue.

14
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,560
You were pretty quick
taking my clothes off just now.

15
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:13,799
Why now...?

16
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,400
Miss Lin. What are you doing here?

17
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:23,640
I knew it. He's bad news.

18
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,560
Ningxue.

19
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:26,840
It's not that.

20
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,959
Save it.

21
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:29,159
I saw everything.

22
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:32,159
We're not even a thing anyway.

23
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,640
Who you're with is your call.

24
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,359
Ningxue.

25
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:42,239
Ningxue!

26
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,840
You still have the nerve to chase her?

27
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,439
How long are you planning to play her?

28
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,159
Ningxue's naive.

29
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:50,000
I'm not that easy to fool.

30
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,560
Disgusting.

31
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:54,159
Ningxue.

32
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:57,120
Miss Lin looks all cold and aloof.

33
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,680
Didn't think she'd be this childish.

34
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,719
Men's business,

35
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,879
and she wants in?

36
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,920
Go tell Gu Yuanbing.

37
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,520
I can let the past slide,

38
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:14,159
but if he messes with the Lin family
or Ningxue again,

39
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,560
I'll make him disappear for good.

40
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,479
Su Wubing.

41
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,159
What are you doing here?

42
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,719
The master sent us

43
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,000
to bring you back.

44
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,719
Get up first.

45
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:32,879
Miss.

46
00:02:33,319 --> 00:02:34,520
We know you've suffered a lot

47
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,919
in the Su family all these years.

48
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,520
These... and these...

49
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,199
are from the master,

50
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,960
to make up

51
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,199
for everything the Su family's done.

52
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,520
What does he even want?

53
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,400
Please come back with us.

54
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,039
The master said

55
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,080
as long as you return,

56
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,560
everything in the Fang family
will be yours.

57
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,719
I'm not going back.

58
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:54,319
I'm doing just fine with the Su family.

59
00:02:57,639 --> 00:02:59,360
If you won't get up, then stay kneeling.

60
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,919
I'm not leaving either way.

61
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:02,960
Miss.

62
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,639
Please, we're begging you.

63
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:07,520
Back then the master had to
keep the Fang line going.

64
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:09,439
That's why he begged your mother

65
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,759
to send you away.

66
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,560
Now he's getting old.

67
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,159
He just wants to be with you again.

68
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,360
Could it be someone's here?

69
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,039
Fang Tian.

70
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:31,400
Wubing.

71
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,199
Who are you people?

72
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:41,159
You guys should go, now.

73
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,000
Head back first.

74
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,439
Goodbye.

75
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:54,599
They were...?

76
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:58,719
Mom's asleep. Keep it down.
Come with me.

77
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,479
Wait for me.

78
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,479
Wubing.

79
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,919
Open it.

80
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,879
I saved it for you.

81
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,480
I heard it's good for your health.

82
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,879
This spirit ginseng looks
at least 800 years old.

83
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,120
Even Herbal Hall can barely get this.

84
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,480
Where'd you get it?

85
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,240
Those people just now gave it to me.

86
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:38,399
They said I'm from the Fang family

87
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,240
and want me to go back with them.

88
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,800
The Fang family?

89
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,079
When did they first reach out?

90
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,519
Before Mom was hospitalized.

91
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:52,560
They said they sent me away back then

92
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,759
because of family rivalries.

93
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:57,040
Wubing, I don't want to go back.

94
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,680
I just want to stay with you and Mom.

95
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,199
Oh, you.

96
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,079
You've never known
who your real parents were.

97
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,120
Now that they've found you,

98
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,920
might as well go see them.

99
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,240
Even Mom

100
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,879
would be happy for you.

101
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:14,639
Wubing.

102
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,639
Wait.

103
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:18,959
Wubing.

104
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,920
I know you only have eyes for Ningxue,

105
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,720
but I just want to stay by your side.

106
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,360
I don't care about any Fang family.

107
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:31,319
As long as you don't push me away,

108
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,759
I'll stay with you forever.

109
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,560
Why would I ever push you away?

110
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,120
Blood is thicker than water.

111
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,600
You'll have to go back someday.

112
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,319
But...

113
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,240
No buts.

114
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,319
Get some sleep.

115
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:10,360
Miss, Mr. Su is at the door.

116
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:11,360
Not seeing him.

117
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:16,759
But Mr. Lin said we should treat him...

118
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,839
Should what?

119
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,160
I said no.

120
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,160
Tell him I'm not here.

121
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,000
You can go.

122
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,639
Yes.

123
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,439
Why do I feel like

124
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,759
you're even madder than I am?

125
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,759
Of course I am.

126
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,920
Who does he think he is, lecturing me?

127
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,120
And on top of that,

128
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,879
he was with another woman
behind your back...

129
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,240
After I calmed down last night,

130
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,360
I thought it through.

131
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,920
He's not that kind of guy.

132
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:43,959
Maybe...

133
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:45,920
it really was a misunderstanding.

134
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,560
Don't tell me you've
actually fallen for him.

135
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,399
We literally saw him walk out

136
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:53,480
of the same room with Jiang Yao.

137
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,680
How could that be fake?

138
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,839
I don't know.

139
00:06:56,759 --> 00:06:58,000
But I can't shake the feeling

140
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,399
that we're destined to be together.

141
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,160
Every time I have no other way out,

142
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,680
he shows up.

143
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,439
Even if his timing is always strange.

144
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:11,199
I don't care if you want to trust him.

145
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:14,040
But I'm not letting this slide.

146
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,160
Next time I see him,

147
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:18,240
I'm making him pay.

148
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,839
Feel good?

149
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:25,959
Not bad.

150
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:29,319
But then he just left.

151
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,560
He figured it out?

152
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,000
Relax.

153
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:36,600
We ran into Lin Ningxue at the door.

154
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:38,959
She was furious.

155
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:39,800
For real?

156
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,839
Of course.

157
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,199
You should've seen her face.

158
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:49,360
Not bad.

159
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,040
As long as Ningxue and
Su Wubing fall out,

160
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:55,000
no one's backing the Lin family anymore.

161
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,360
Let's see how they fight me then.

162
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,360
Mr. Gu.

163
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:04,759
I pulled this off for you.

164
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,560
Don't I deserve a reward?

165
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,279
What kind of reward do you want?

166
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,959
I want...

167
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,120
Who's there?

168
00:09:13,038 --> 00:09:17,141
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

169
00:09:17,141 --> 00:09:21,861
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

170
00:09:21,861 --> 00:09:26,741
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

171
00:09:26,741 --> 00:09:31,861
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

172
00:09:31,861 --> 00:09:36,261
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

173
00:09:36,261 --> 00:09:40,941
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

174
00:09:40,941 --> 00:09:46,341
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

175
00:09:46,341 --> 00:09:52,735
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
